        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Gloriosissimis <expan><abbr>beatissimisq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> martyribus qui <expan><abbr>persecutione</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> Diocletiani et Maximian<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied> <lb n="2"/>divinis legibus passi sunt quorum corpora hoc loco deposita aput <note>sic</note> Deum in aeternum manen<supplied reason="lost">t</supplied> <lb n="3"/>his cui <note>sic</note> divinitus inspirare hoc in animo dignatus est nomina eorum venerandaque <lb n="4"/>corpora anaclitis <note>sic</note> lapideis <note>sic</note> cum hermulis adque <note>sic</note> mensa conclusit unde divin<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> clemen<lb break="no" n="5"/>tiae cum suis omnibus gratias agit qui memoriae martyrum merita exoptata <lb n="6"/>vota conplevit felix semper vivat qui intentissime legerit <lb n="7"/>felicior qui Deo Omnipotenti per C<expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>ristum</abbr></expan> eius tota fide craediderit <note>sic</note>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p/>
            </div>
